---
import Badge from "../ui/Badge.astro";
import Button from "../ui/Button.astro";
import Container from "../ui/Container.astro";
---

<section class="overflow-hidden pb-18 pt-16 sm:pb-24 sm:pt-20">
  <Container className="grid items-center gap-12 lg:grid-cols-[1.04fr_0.96fr]">
    <div>
      <Badge>Open-source deployment platform in active development</Badge>
      <h1
        class="mt-7 text-4xl font-semibold leading-tight tracking-tight text-ink sm:text-6xl"
      >
        Deploy project dari Git ke URL publik tanpa ribet server.
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-6 max-w-xl text-lg leading-8 text-muted">
        Sakala membantu mahasiswa, developer pemula, dan tim kecil menjalankan
        aplikasi tanpa harus memahami VPS, SSL, reverse proxy, dan setup
        infrastruktur manual sejak hari pertama.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-9 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
        <Button href="https://github.com/gmedia" external>Lihat GitHub</Button>
        <Button href="/docs" variant="secondary">Baca Dokumentasi</Button>
        <Button href="https://app.sakala.dev" variant="ghost"
          >Masuk ke Dashboard</Button
        >
      </div>
    </div>
    <div
      class="rounded-3xl border border-border bg-surface p-4 shadow-[0_24px_64px_-40px_rgba(15,118,110,.4)] sm:p-6"
    >
      <div
        class="rounded-2xl bg-terminal px-5 py-5 text-sm text-terminal-text sm:p-7"
      >
        <div class="mb-6 flex gap-2">
          <span class="size-3 rounded-full bg-error/80"></span>
          <span class="size-3 rounded-full bg-warning/80"></span>
          <span class="size-3 rounded-full bg-success/80"></span>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-4 font-mono text-[13px] leading-6 sm:text-sm">
          <p><span class="text-primary-soft">$</span> git push origin main</p>
          <p><span class="text-success">✓</span> Repository diterima</p>
          <p>
            <span class="text-primary-soft">→</span> Menyiapkan deployment aplikasi...
          </p>
          <p><span class="text-success">✓</span> Routing publik siap</p>
          <p class="rounded-lg bg-terminal-soft px-4 py-3 text-primary-soft">
            demo.run.sakala.dev
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p
        class="mt-4 rounded-xl bg-accent-soft px-4 py-3 text-sm leading-6 text-ink"
      >
        Sakala masih dalam tahap pengembangan aktif. Saat ini fokus kami adalah
        membangun pengalaman deployment yang sederhana, transparan, dan ramah
        untuk pembelajaran.
      </p>
    </div>
  </Container>
</section>
